author: gstein
msg: Adjust test #34 to be prepared for different output under wc-ng. Some
underlying bugs are present in the "svn update" process, but wc-1 uses
other bugs to compensate and still manage to do the right thing. wc-ng has
no such luxury, so the output changes.
See the discussion in the comments, and the thread at:
http://svn.haxx.se/dev/archive-2009-04/0760.shtml
* subversion/tests/cmdline/update_tests.py:
(update_with_obstructing_additions): leave a hojillion comments and
tweak the output when running under wc-ng.
